snippet.title: NARC SHIELD: NARCISSISTIC ABUSE AWARENESS
snippet.description:
#narcissist #narcissism 

I am here to speak on #Narcissistic relationships and a survivor. I believe it is important to have support when in a toxic relationship. People who have not been in these relationships have a hard time understanding and can cause you to feel more alone without meaning to. I believe in getting good therapy and learning more about yourself to heal. I have understanding having gone through it myself and still learning every day. 
It feels like you will never heal once you leave one of these relationships but you can. It does take time. ❤️
Click discussion for more. 


Disclaimer: I am not a therapist: I can’t diagnose anyone for certain (in my videos or elsewhere) and these are my observations and opinions based on the knowledge I have gained in becoming a survivor of abuse. 

Please subscribe to my channel for alerts to new content. Like and share 😃
